Shrew-gallery 1.0

============================
* Compilation / Installation
============================


Under Linux, enter the shrew-gallery directory, then simply type:

	make

then, copy the file name "out/index.php" in the directory containing your images. 

If you want to restrain the acess of the gallery, create a file name "access.php" in the same directory.
You can see the example in the "examples" directiory.

You can add a file named "all.zip" in the same directory to allow download of all images.


